These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, videographer, dancer
1. the videographer is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | videographer | dancer | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, entrepreneur, bartender
1. the bartender is on the far right##1
2. the musician is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | musician | entrepreneur | bartender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, gardening, chess
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | singing | gardening | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, malaysian
1. the colombian is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | malaysian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, tea
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | milk | 7up | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski, subway
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | subway | jet-ski | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, crime, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | drama | crime |

